  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The on-site inspection fee for auditors and experts set forth in Item 2, Subparagraph 4 of the preceding article shall apply mutatis mutandis to the Directions for the Overseas Travel Allowance Disbursement, and shall be charged from the audited unit by the central competent authority.]]></條文內容>
